    ELet ws1 kind b p ws2 e1 ws3 e2 ws4   -> replaceE__ eidCleared (ELet ws1 kind b (clearPIds p) ws2 e1 ws3 e2 ws4)
    EFun ws1 pats body ws2                -> replaceE__ eidCleared (EFun ws1 (List.map clearPIds pats) body ws2)
